{"tid":1835662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以後見到戴口罩嘅獅子狗 同佢講: 戴口罩就係支持暴徒!","createTime":"2020-01-23T02:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T14:41:44.000Z","uid":225100,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a16338dd549917f5ede068c3c6c21d48d91612f0","tid":1835662,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足朋友話<br />\n今日響街見到隻戴緊口罩嘅撕紙廢老<br />\n二話不說就影鳩佢相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後同隻廢老講:<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔洗驚wor 黨會保護你 驚乜肺炎姐?<br />\n咪戴口罩阿<br />\n戴口罩就係支持暴徒!</span><br />\n<br />\n個廢老追咗手足兩條街<br />\n係咁講埋啲廢話: <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">關你咩事阿 你做咩影我相</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後朋友繼續挑機回應:<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">你又要撕又要戴口罩支持暴徒<br />\n係唔係精神分裂阿</span><br />\n<br />\n點知個廢老即刻惱羞成怒<br />\n一野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">除咗自己個口罩</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">驚咩 我 我先冇驚 我病咗先戴 關你咩事</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正當手足想再影佢嘅時候<br />\n廢老今次真係郁手想一野推埋去<br />\n由於手足係和理非 又趕住返工<br />\n所以只好戰略性撤退<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>戴口罩就是支持暴徒</strong></span><br />\n#人一藍 #物種演化"},{"pid":"2d62926dde0447b4571bad6250bc66b2b2da8db0","tid":1835662,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:24:34.000Z","msg":"要叫晒身邊朋友戴口罩阿<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"269f616ee1a0acdb62c32641c8d5907ac2e4987b","tid":1835662,"uid":88032,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:24:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br 